</h3><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-295_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-0df5dd66-e51e-4677-9cf6-5ef95da91362"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Rolling out PSIRF (Patient Safety Incident Response Framework), promoting transparency and learning.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-298_">Mental health integration
</h3><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-300_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-d086b1f0-64d3-4658-a8b9-756a7a390a14"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">Blending mental and physical health into primary, community, and acute services.
</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bhqpXc bptxD pf-303_">Benefits of NHS Foundation Trust status</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-dISoPS kgxkyr pf-305_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-306_"><strong>Responsive local services</strong> - Tailored to population needs</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-308_"><strong>Democratic participation</strong> - Staff and public co-governance</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-310_"><strong>Financial innovation</strong> - Faster capital investment and service redesign</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-312_"><strong>Reduced bureaucracy</strong> - Local autonomy accelerates decision-making</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-eONOlN iAhVxb pf-314_"><strong>Community Trust</strong> - Deep accountability to those they serve.
</li></ul><p class="sc-fPrdjK bLmLvT pf-316_" data-pf-type="Paragraph4"><input type="checkbox" id="compact-bb3f5b12-56c5-4531-a62c-7ab896c25341"/><span class="pf-paragraph-content ">These advantages have made Foundation Trusts leading lights in NHS reform, with many topping national performance rankings and spearheading innovation.
